title: Incredible Value! Love This Location! Lovely 1Bed/1Bath Apartment Home
posting_body: ['Welcome to The VUE in Kirkland, WA', "At The Vue, in Kirkland, WA, you'll find comfortable living combined with a smart and functional apartment layout, amenities that make your life easier, and enough room to stretch your legs.", "With walk-in closets, fully equipped kitchens with energy-efficient appliances, and in-home washers and dryer, we're sure to give you everything you need in your new apartment and more.", 'Take a dip in the seasonal swimming pool when the heat of summer kicks into high gear.', 'If getting in the water isn’t your speed, relax with a magazine on the oversized sundeck.', 'Our clubhouse offers complimentary WiFi, so posting pictures on Instagram and returning emails is a breeze.', 'Both you and your pet will enjoy strolling down our walking trails and along the meditation and wildlife pond.', 'Call today to schedule a personalized tour of our community and find out just how perfect The Vue is for you!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 552 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- In-Home Washer & Dryer', '- Mirrored Sliding Closet Doors*', '- Ceiling Fans', '- Hardwood Inspired Flooring', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Lovely Views', '- Private Patios/Balconies', '- Energy-Efficient Appliances', '- Stainless-Steel Appliances*', '- New Kitchen Countertops & Cabinets', '- Fully Equipped Kitchen', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Business Center', '- Near Transit, Major Employers, Colleges & Shops', '- Greenbelt-Protected Community', '- Oversized Sundeck', '- Fitness Center', '- Clubhouse with Complimentary WiFi Access', '- Online Rental Payments', '- Barbecue', '- Seasonal Swimming Pool', '- Pet Friendly', '- Parcel Pending Package Delivery Service', '- Pet-Walking Trails', '- Onsite Management', '- Meditation & Wildlife Pond', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, fees and restrictions apply.', 'Contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday -
